testcase.name: Room disconnect should set the Room's LocalParticipant's .state to "disconnected"
Room disconnect should not change the Room's .participants Map
Room disconnect should not change Room's RemoteParticipant's .states
Room disconnect should not change Room's Participant's .tracks
Room disconnect should not change Room's Participant's .trackPublications
Room disconnect should raise a "participantDisconnected" event for every other RemoteParticipant connected to the Room
Room disconnect should raise a "unsubscribed" event on each RemoteParticipant's RemoteTrackPublicationss
Room disconnect should raise a "trackUnsubscribed" event for each RemoteParticipant's RemoteTracks
Room getStats includes the expected LocalAudioTrackStats and LocalVideoTrackStats
Room getStats includes the expected RemoteAudioTrackStats and RemoteVideoTrackStats
Room "disconnected" event is raised whenever the LocalParticipant is disconnected via the REST API
Room "dominantSpeakerChanged" event is raised whenever the dominant speaker in the Room changes
Room "participantConnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant connects to the Room
Room "participantConnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant connects to the Room and should add the RemoteParticipant to the Room's .participants Map
Room "participantConnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant connects to the Room and should set the RemoteParticipant's .state to "connected"
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should delete the RemoteParticipant from the Room's .participants Map
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should set the RemoteParticipant's .state to "disconnected"
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should not change the RemoteParticipant's .tracks
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should not change Room's Participant's .trackPublications
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should raise a "unsubscribed" event on each RemoteParticipant's RemoteTrackPublicationss
Room "participantDisconnected" event is raised whenever a RemoteParticipant disconnects from the Room and should fire the "trackUnsubscribed" event for the RemoteParticipant's RemoteTracks
Room "recordingStarted" event is raised whenever recording is started on the Room via the REST API
Room "recordingStopped" event is raised whenever recording is stopped on the Room via the REST API
